metadata.description: Remember the 1960's with this original hand-painted, one of a kind, 12.5" x 10.5" cartoon cell of the Pink Panther driving Wilma Flintstone.  Actually used in the production of a cartoon. Painted on a clear substrate and photographed on black background, but it can be framed with any background color.  Makes a wonderful gift!  Winning bid includes mailing of the physical cell to you, NFT certificate and digital image!
